# Frontend — Next.js 14 (App Router)

- Pages and layouts under `app/` — route groups `(marketing)`, `(auth)`, `(app)`, `widget/`; files `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`.
- Components and types: `PascalCase`; functions and variables: `camelCase`.
- Styles: Tailwind in JSX; do not add new CSS frameworks without a strong reason; match existing spacing and UI patterns.
- API data: reuse existing helpers and `fetch` patterns — avoid duplicate wrappers without cause.
